# Public Assets Directory

This directory contains static assets for the documentation site:

- `/logos/` - Logo files and brand assets
- `/images/` - Screenshots, diagrams, and other images
- `/downloads/` - Downloadable files (if any)

Place your HappyCMDB logo files here:
- `happycmdb-logo.svg` - Main logo for navigation
- `happycmdb-hero.svg` - Hero image for homepage
- `favicon.svg` / `favicon.png` - Favicon
- `og-image.png` - Open Graph image for social sharing (1200x630px recommended)
